import React, { useState } from 'react'
import FooterSection from '../sections/FooterSection'
import MainMenuSection from '../sections/MainMenuSection'
import ShowCase from '../sections/ShowCase'
import UnderShowCase from '../sections/UnderShowCase'
import ProductGridSection from '../sections/ProductGridSection'
import TopPicks from '../sections/TopPicks'
import CategoryRightSection from '../sections/CategoryRightSection'
import CategoryLeftSection from '../sections/CategoryRightSection'


const HomeView = () => {

  window.top.document.title = 'Fixxo.'


  const [featuredProducts, setFeaturedProducts] = useState ([
    { id: 1, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/1146242/pexels-photo-1146242.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-olga-1146242.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 2, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/1154638/pexels-photo-1154638.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-nappy-1154638.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 3, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/936079/pexels-photo-936079.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-nappy-936079.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 4, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/667208/pexels-photo-667208.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-leah-kelley-667208.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 5, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/936102/pexels-photo-936102.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-nappy-936102.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 6, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/106255/pexels-photo-106255.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-kasuma-106255.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 7, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/968571/pexels-photo-968571.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-igor-link-968571.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 8, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/932402/pexels-photo-932402.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-godisable-jacob-932402.jpg&fm=jpg"}
  ])
  const [topProducts, setTopProducts] = useState([
    { id: 9, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/936102/pexels-photo-936102.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-nappy-936102.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 10, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/106255/pexels-photo-106255.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-kasuma-106255.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 11, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/968571/pexels-photo-968571.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-igor-link-968571.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 12, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/932402/pexels-photo-932402.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-godisable-jacob-932402.jpg&fm=jpg"}
  ])
  const [LeftProducts, setLeftProducts] = useState([
    { id: 13, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/936102/pexels-photo-936102.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-nappy-936102.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 14, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/106255/pexels-photo-106255.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-kasuma-106255.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 15, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/968571/pexels-photo-968571.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-igor-link-968571.jpg&fm=jpg"},
    { id: 16, name: "Modern Black Blouse", category: "Fashion", price: "$35.00", rating: 5, img: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/932402/pexels-photo-932402.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-godisable-jacob-932402.jpg&fm=jpg"}
  ])

  return (
    <>
      <MainMenuSection />
      <ShowCase />
      <ProductGridSection  title="Featured Products" products={featuredProducts} />
      <TopPicks/>
      <CategoryRightSection  title="Top Products" products={topProducts}/>
      
      <FooterSection />
    </>
  )

export default HomeView
